I'm slowly preparing for a few possible outcomes of the next few months or years, in the way Scorpios do. 

November will be where any big decisions that have to be made have to be made. Doing a few test runs for things in this era: seeing how much things cost in cafes etc.

I don't know what's worse at this cafe: the guy clearing his throat every 20 seconds or the girl crunching chips slowly one at a time, and she just started the plate of chips.

Do you not know the universal signal for "pipe down" which is repeated stares as you clear and crunch?

The most perfect moments I love having to myself are the moments I have sitting in front of a cafe, alone. Watching the world pass by and just enjoying every inch of the silence that slowly inches itâ€™s way towards my heart and my mind.
